the team lead feedback is read. But &quot;reading and implementing are two different things.&quot;<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Disguises:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>No disguises.<br><br>Scott: It came down to 2 alternatives. Make disguises purely cosmetic...or make everyone else unhappy...you could say [because we're faced with these alternative]...it's &quot;tabled indefinitely.&quot;<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> What's the status with left axe? Is it a secret nerf?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>It's definitely not done on purpose. We'll [Sanya and Scott]look into it.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> What races and classes are in the expansion?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: Details aren't being given out. Screenshots will be released in July. However some info: New city for each realm, new &quot;surroundings&quot; for the city (outdoor zones etc), 1 new race per realm, new classes for each realm.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Will the new engine be available to all or just the expansion?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: Just expansion. It's an entire new game...as big as the present game. They've hired the developer from Morrowind to do water effects etc. Players with the old version of the game will be able to see the new races etc but not be one.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Update on spellcrafting?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Spell crafting is our number one priority behind Mordred.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Tradeskill updates?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: New one are planned constantly. &quot;There is a big gaping whole in the economy where spell crafting will be.&quot;<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Update on Mordred?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Almost ready to go<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Will we get player owned horses?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: &quot;We want them eventually&quot;. They tried once so far but did not have a &quot;successful implementation&quot;.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Guilds</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Artwork for guild housing has all been finished. Housing will be worked on after spellcrafting. A guild vault was attempted but they had problems implementing it.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Arena, dueling</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>No ETA on arenas. &quot;It's a question of time and resources&quot;<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Will collision detection ever be implemented?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Scott: No, not in the existing game. It causes people to get stuck and to fall through the world. Maybe in an expansion.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Will RP servers ever have CSR run events?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: No events, no staff right now. We tried once with volunteers but it didn't work and its hard with volunteers and we prefer to pay our employees.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Will more emotes be added?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>On the &quot;to do list&quot;<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> What happened to the story contest?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: &quot;Sanya is a loser&quot; -- Sanya said I could quote her on that. She needs to contact the people who won.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Will your rant page ever be updated?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: ::laughs:: the page &quot;keeps her honest&quot;. No update planned but maybe.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> And I asked this just for Elaa: Is Mythic hiring developers? Are you single?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Sanya: No. We literally don't have room. Scott is working in a closet. No ::laughs::<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> What's the most played class in game?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>Scott: Cleric followed by armsman. For Hibernia only it's druid, for Midgard, Thane.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> What realms do you play?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>We can't really answer that but it's pretty even company wide. Scott: &quot;But I play a Nightshade so...&quot; Sanya: And I played in Midgard but my main is in Albion right now.<br><br>That's all I got to in the time allowed. If I didn't get to your question I'm sorry  I didn't have much time to prepare and to sort through the questions - I had to skim a lot of the longer worded ones.<br><br>Next year I'll be sure to be more prepared and open it up to questions earlier now that I know that I can get an interview set up.<br><br>For more E3 reports see the Logged Out forum for 2 picture posts from me and 3 from Wix. I'll also be writing up detailed info on Shadowbane, NeverWinter Nights and the Sims Online.<br><br>Most of this will also be up on my offlinetshirts.com site as well if you ever loose track of the threads.<br><br>-------------<br><br>PS<br><br>Additional info gleaned from talking to Mythic folks at their booth:<br><br>They will be expanding all dungeons.<br><br>There will be underwater zones in the expansion (Shrouded Isles).<br><br>There will be 5-10 new outdoor zones in the expansion.<br><br>==============================================<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=1143.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=1143.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1143.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=1143.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This 